Package: matrixio-kernel-modules-buster
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 matrixio-creator-init,
 raspberrypi-kernel-headers,
 raspberrypi-kernel,
 dkms,
Description: Matrix Creator kernel modules for Raspbian Buster
 This package provides DKMS source for MATRIX Creator kernel modules
 optimized for Raspbian Buster (Debian 10.13).
 .
 Supports:
  - Raspberry Pi 4 Model B Rev 1.4 (BCM2711) with 5.10.103-v7l+ kernel (ARM32)
  - Legacy Raspberry Pi systems with 5.10.x kernel series
 .
 The package includes kernel modules for:
  - Core MFD functionality (matrixio-core)
  - Audio codec support (matrixio-codec, matrixio-mic, matrixio-playback)
  - Environmental sensors (matrixio-env, matrixio-imu)
  - LED ring control (matrixio-everloop)
  - GPIO interface (matrixio-gpio)
  - UART interface (matrixio-uart)
  - Register map interface (matrixio-regmap)
 .
 This legacy package maintains compatibility with older kernel APIs
 and is specifically designed for production Pi 4 systems.